Now seriously... 

{{sticker:sg-zephyr}}

I am totally fucked up!

{{champion:202}} 
Jhin mains this patch: "How dare you remove the interaction!"

Jhin mains after seeing pbe: "#ART"

TBH as an ADC main since S1 i really would love if {{item:3153}} became a core starter item for ADCs, i always hated that all the other classes had their perfect first buy that gave them all the stats they need like 
Fighters {{item:3071}} / {{item:3074}}  / {{item:3748}} 
Mages {{item:3285}} (Morello before that) / {{item:3027}}  
Assassins {{item:3142}} / {{item:3147}} / {{item:3146}} 
Tanks {{item:3068}} / {{item:3065}} 

While most adcs first "item" is basically {{item:1038}} +{{item:3086}}  
Not sure why,just never liked the fact that they have to buy parts of two different items to make a makeshift first item that gives them the stats they need.

On the other hand {{item:3153}} is basically that first and core item that gives them the stats they need,ofcourse in reality it's not worth delaying your {{item:3031}} +{{item:3087}}  due to the fact that those two scale much better with one another and obviously give you more damage compared to going {{item:3153}} {{item:3087}} ,but now that Botrk price is going down,along with IE not being as effective against squishies,especially early game when true damage isn't as worth due to low armor i believe and hope that {{item:3153}} will be making a comeback
